cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language processing, specifically Chinese sentiment analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a neural network model, which suggests it could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves text classification, which could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper uses multiple representations of Chinese text, which could be related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
